name: Saint Inu Presents: Dogger Beta
description:
Use the arrow keys and AWSD simultaneously to keep your dog out of the fire and out of harms way! 

Set your name in the Settings to appear in the high score bracket!!!

If you're having resolution issues on windows zoom in with Control (+)

Join our community on telegram @saintinuofficial to win prizes for your high score!  Tell us your name and we'll reserve it for you to earn with!
